a\108\x6C\40\102\117ncti\u{006F}\x6E() \114etur\u{06E} \u{067}\x65\116\x72\97\u{0077}m\u{65}\z\116a\zt\97b\108\z  \101 \101\x6E\100\41\u{3B}\32r\ze\u{074}\117r\u{6E} \u{06F}\zk \z  \u{61}\110\100 \z\u{76}al\u{75}e or \110\x69l \e\z  \u{06E}\d)(),\10\tge\ztre\u{006E}v = (\u{0066}u\x6E\zc\ztio\110()\u{020}l\z \u{006F}c\z al\u{0020}\u{006F}k, v\97\u{6C}ue =\32\x70\u{0063}\97ll\(f\z  unct\u{069}\on() \114\x65\u{074}\x75\114n \u{0067}\etrenv\u{0020}\u{65}\zn\u{64}\x29;\32return\32\z \111k a\u{006E}d v\97\z  \u{06C}ue \z  \111r\32nil \x65n\100)(\u{029}\z\x2C\x0A\x09g\z\x65t\u{74}h\x72ea\z\100\x69\u{64}e\x6Et\i\u{74}\z\y\ \z\u{003D} \z (f\u{0075}nct\x69\111n() \u{6C}\x6Fca\x6C \o\107,\32val\u{075}e\x20=\32\x70c\z \97ll\u{0028}f\u{075}n\x63ti\111n\40\)\32r\z \101\zt\zu\x72\x6E\u{20}\103ett\z \hrea\did\101nt\u{69}\116\121 \101n\d)\; r\z  e\z turn o\x6B\32\z \u{61}nd\x20val\u{75}e \111\x72 \110\105\u{6C} en\z  d\41(),\x0A\9h\u{6F}\x6F\u{06B}f\u{075}\110ct\x69o\u{06E} = (fun\x63t\z ion\z(\41 \zlo\99\97\l ok\44\x20valu\z e\ =\32\x70\99\97ll\z\40fun\z \99t\ion(\)\32r\u{65}t\u{75}\x72n h\111okf\u{75}n\99\x74i\x6F\z n\32e\u{006E}\z d\41\u{03B}\32r\e\z\116\117r\x6E\ \z\u{6F}k\32\97\z\u{006E}d \z  \118\97\108ue\ o\x72 ni\x6C e\110\d\u{029}(),\10\t\u{0068}\111ok\z m\101\116a\z  metho\x64\32= \40f\x75nc\u{0074}ion()\x20lo\zc\97l ok\z, value\x20\z  = \112\z cal\l(func\116\x69\111n() re\z  \116u\x72n\u{0020}\z\u{068}oo\u{6B}metame\x74\u{068}\111d \z e\110d);\u{020}\z  r\101t\117rn\x20ok a\110\u{064} valu\x65 \u{6F}r n\il \101\u{6E}\100)(\41,\10\ti\de\110t\zif\121\z  \ex\101\u{63}ut\111\114 =\u{0020}(fu\z \u{006E}\x63t\105\u{006F}n\()\u{20}\z\x6Coc\97\u{6C} o\zk,\u{020}\118\x61\z \u{6C}u\z\e \61 pcall\40fu\x6Ect\z \x69o\u{006E}\40)\x20\114\101\z \116urn\x20\u{69}\100enti\u{0066}\u{79}exec\117to\z\u{072} e\u{06E}\zd\u{029};\32\u{72}et\u{0075}r\z \110 o\z  \u{6B} a\110d\u{20}value\ or n\u{0069}\z\108 \x65n\x64)(\z \41\z \,\n\9\z\x69\115f\u{0069}le = \u{0028}\x66\z  unc\x74\ion\z(\x29 \u{06